02:53.970 --> 02:55.672
Yeah, me too.

02:55.805 --> 02:58.808
Well, uh...

03:01.944 --> 03:03.412
...just wanted to, uh,
talk to you,

03:03.546 --> 03:06.281
you know, and see
how you're doing and, uh--

03:06.415 --> 03:07.884
Why?

03:08.017 --> 03:10.385
Well, I just...

03:16.191 --> 03:18.293
Look, I know. uh...

03:18.427 --> 03:20.395
