I am so, so sorry.

03:26.869 --> 03:29.539
Are you fucking serious
right now?

03:29.672 --> 03:31.007
What?

03:31.140 --> 03:32.141
What the hell is
wrong with you?

03:32.274 --> 03:33.442
Nothing's wrong with me.

03:33.576 --> 03:37.345
I'm just-- I'm, uh--
just wanted--

03:37.479 --> 03:39.649
What makes you think that
I want to hear that?

03:39.782 --> 03:44.419
Why is-- Why is now the time
for me to hear that?

03:44.554 --> 03:45.722
Come on, honey.

03:45.855 --> 03:47.222
