of times before,

03:47.355 --> 03:48.591
and you didn't pick up
and I--

03:48.725 --> 03:49.992
So it's my fault?

03:50.126 --> 03:51.594
No, it's no one's fault.
It's no one's fault.

03:51.728 --> 03:56.132
I just, uh--
I'm here.

03:56.264 --> 03:57.265
You're here now?

03:57.399 --> 03:59.001
Are you fucking kidding me?

03:59.135 --> 04:00.636
No, I'm not kidding. Okay?

04:00.770 --> 04:02.538
I am trying to say I'm sorry.

04:02.672 --> 04:04.140
I am trying to apologize.

04:04.272 --> 04:06.509
I'm trying to fix this mistake.

04:06.642 --> 04:09.078
