05:35.264 --> 05:38.601
Stop.

05:42.905 --> 05:45.808
Oh, no,
no, no, no.

05:46.309 --> 05:48.578
Wait, wait--
Please!

05:54.183 --> 05:57.053
No! Ah!

06:13.669 --> 06:15.905
No!

10:25.555 --> 10:27.456
-Jocelyn.
-Pastor Lewis.

10:27.591 --> 10:28.390
Thank you again.

10:28.525 --> 10:29.692
It was a lovely service.

10:29.825 --> 10:31.561
Of course.

10:31.694 --> 10:34.363
If you need anything,
please don't hesitate to ask.

10:34.497 --> 10:37.366
Thank you.

10:46.709 --> 10:48.077
Hey, JC.

10:48.210 --> 10:50.146
Hey, guys.

10:51.515 --> 10:52.448
Thanks for coming.

10:52.582 --> 10:53.749
Of course.

10:53.883 --> 10:55.284
If you need anything,
let us know.

10:55.417 --> 10:56.819
Thank you.

10:56.952 --> 10:58.354
Is that her?

11:00.656 --> 11:04.326
- Yeah, it is.
- Huh.

11:04.760 --> 11:07.263
I'm surprised she came.

11:08.330 --> 11:09.899
Yeah, me too.

11:17.773 --> 11:19.141
Hey, sweetie.

11:19.275 --> 11:20.276
Hey, Mom.

11:20.409 --> 11:21.377
How are you?

11:21.511 --> 11:22.845
I'm okay.

11:22.978 --> 11:26.415
Just wanted to let you know
that it's done.

11:26.550 --> 11:27.816
The service is over.

11:27.950 --> 11:30.286
Oh, okay.

11:30.419 --> 11:31.420
How was it?

11:31.555 --> 11:33.989
