about how you're doing.

11:43.365 --> 11:45.701
I'm fine. Really.

11:45.834 --> 11:46.702
Yeah?

11:46.835 --> 11:48.538
And how's Maryland?

11:48.672 --> 11:51.941
Well, I leave in two days,
so I'm looking forward to that.

11:52.074 --> 11:52.775
