12:15.030 --> 12:18.267
Have you talked to Jocelyn?

12:18.434 --> 12:22.037
Um, yeah, we talked.

12:22.338 --> 12:23.305
Yeah?

12:23.439 --> 12:24.440
How'd that go?

12:24.574 --> 12:26.710
I don't know, it was short.

12:26.842 --> 12:28.277
