12:34.718 --> 12:37.886
Well, that might be good.

12:38.153 --> 12:40.289
Well,
I don't think I'm gonna go.

12:40.422 --> 12:42.157
Okay.

12:42.291 --> 12:44.426
I mean, if that's
what you're comfortable with.

12:44.994 --> 12:46.895
I just don't see the point.

12:47.029 --> 12:47.930
I get that.

12:48.063 --> 12:49.633
Trust me, I do.

12:49.765 --> 12:54.770
