she lost him, too, Em.

12:55.371 --> 12:58.140
It might be good to just hear
what she has to say.

12:58.274 --> 13:00.109
At least this one time.

13:02.244 --> 13:05.414
Look, you just do what's best
for you, okay?

13:05.848 --> 13:07.983
Uh, yeah.

13:11.086 --> 13:14.390
