okay?

13:15.858 --> 13:17.326
Yeah I will.

13:17.459 --> 13:19.862
All right. Love you, Em.

13:19.995 --> 13:22.831
Love you.

13:40.215 --> 13:41.984
- Hey, buddy!
- What're you doin?

13:43.218 --> 13:44.119
