16:26.081 --> 16:29.485
If you can still hear me,
please stay on the line.

16:55.344 --> 16:56.579
-Sorry!
-Sorry!

17:29.946 --> 17:32.949
-Hey.
-Hey.

17:33.315 --> 17:35.852
You want anything to drink?

17:35.985 --> 17:37.754
