I'll pose for a photo.

18:34.242 --> 18:38.047
And then he turns around
and drops his pants

18:38.180 --> 18:39.181
all the way to the ground

18:39.314 --> 18:40.717
and just flashes
his ass at them.

18:40.850 --> 18:42.284
