his mid-life crisis hobbies.

20:03.766 --> 20:04.867
Resent him.

20:05.001 --> 20:06.769
Catch him cheating,
spend the next six months

20:06.903 --> 20:08.437
methodically plotting
his murder.

20:08.571 --> 20:10.973
Send the kids to college.

20:12.508 --> 20:14.977
Like I said, it's all
been planned out.

20:18.380 --> 20:19.649
