24:28.264 --> 24:30.166
Okay.

24:44.347 --> 24:45.982
Hey, Frank.

24:46.115 --> 24:47.917
Hey, JC.

24:51.120 --> 24:52.855
Thanks.

24:54.724 --> 24:57.927
I know it's probably
a stupid question, but...

24:58.461 --> 25:00.463
How you holding up?

25:00.863 --> 25:04.800
I'm hanging in there.

25:04.934 --> 25:08.204
